oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Gay Street
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Gay Street looking south, Knoxville, TN. 1935. Partial view of Riviera Theatre at left, (The Raven with Boris Karloff), McLean's, Gem Drugs, Ath[letic House], Royal Jewelers, Farragut Hotel, Tennessee Theatre. At right, Lane Drugs, Lila's Beauty Shoppe, Comer Studio Photographs, F.W. Woolworth Co. Cars in street.
